-bottom:windowtext 1px solid;border-left:windowtext 1px solid\" width=\"142\" valign=\"top\"><p>178****3986 &nbsp;</p></td></tr><tr><td style=\"border-top:windowtext 1px solid;border-right:windowtext 1px solid;border-bottom:windowtext 1px solid;border-left:windowtext 1px solid\" width=\"127\" valign=\"top\"><p><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">朱家良等</span> &nbsp;</p></td><td style=\"border-top:windowtext 1px solid;border-right:windowtext 1px solid;border-bottom:windowtext 1px solid;border-left:windowtext 1px solid\" width=\"269\" valign=\"top\"><p><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">地球科学学院</span> &nbsp;</p></td><td style=\"border-top:windowtext 1px solid;border-right:windowtext 1px solid;border-bottom:windowtext 1px solid;border-left:windowtext 1px solid\" width=\"142\" valign=\"top\"><p>173****4252 &nbsp;</p></td></tr></tbody></table><p><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">（六）抖音短视频比赛获奖名单</span> &nbsp;</p><table><tbody><tr class=\"firstRow\"><td style=\"border-top:windowtext 1px solid;border-right:windowtext 1px solid;border-bottom:windowtext 1px solid;border-left:windowtext 1px solid\" width=\"97\"><p><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">奖项</span> &nbsp;</p></td><td style=\"border-top:windowtext 1px solid;border-right:windowtext 1px solid;border-bottom:windowtext 1px solid;border-left:windowtext 1px solid\" width=\"127\"><p><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">姓</span>&nbsp; <span style=\"font-family:宋体\">名</span> &nbsp;</p></td><td style=\"border-top:windowtext 1px solid;border-right:windowtext 1px solid;border-bottom:windowtext 1px solid;border-left:windowtext 1px solid\" width=\"269\"><p><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">学</span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <span style=\"font-family:宋体\">院</span> &nbsp;</p></td><td style=\"border-top:windowtext 1px solid;border-right:windowtext 1px solid;border-bottom:windowtext 1px solid;border-left:windowtext 1px solid\" width=\"142\" valign=\"top\"><p><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">手机号码</span> &nbsp;</p></td></tr><tr><td style=\"border-top:windowtext 1px solid;bord