e=\"font-size:16px\">&nbsp; </span><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;line-height:150%\">朱伟林</span><span style=\"font-size:16px\">&nbsp; </span><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;line-height:150%\">邹才能</span> &nbsp;</p><p><strong><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;line-height:150%\">五、会议学术委员会</span></strong> &nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;line-height:150%\">主任：马永生</span><span style=\"font-size:16px\">&nbsp; </span> </p><p><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;line-height:150%\">委员（按拼音升序排列）：</span> &nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;line-height:150%\">包书景</span><span style=\"font-size:16px\"> &nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;line-height:150%\">陈</span><span style=\"font-size:16px\"> &nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;line-height:150%\">勉</span><span style=\"font-size:16px\"> &nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;line-height:150%\">操应长</span><span style=\"font-size:16px\"> &nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;line-height:150%\">董大忠</span><span style=\"font-size:16px\"> &nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;line-height:150%\">付晓飞</span><span style=\"font-size:16px\"> &nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;line-height:150%\">葛洪魁</span><span style=\"font-size:16px\"> &nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;line-height:150%\">郭旭升</span><span style=\"font-size:16px\"> &nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;line-height:150%\">何治亮</span> <span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;line-height:150%\">胡爱梅</span> &nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;line-height:150%\">胡文瑄</span><span style=\"font-size:16px\">&nbsp; </span><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;line-height:150%\">胡望水</span><span style=\"font-size:16px\">&nbsp; </span><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;line-height:150%\">胡宗全</span><span style=\"font-size:16px\">&nbsp; </span><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;line-height:150%\">胡素云</span><span style=\"font-size:16px\">&nbsp; </span><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;line-height:150%\">姜汉桥</span><span style=\"font-size:16px\">&nbsp; </span><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;line-height:150%\">姜振学</span><span style=\"font-size:16px\">&nbsp; </span><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;line-height:150%\">林畅松</span><span style=\"font-size:16px\">&nbsp; </span><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;line-height:150%\">梁建设</span> <span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;line-height:150%\">黎茂稳</span> &nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;line-height:150%\">李建忠</span><span style=\"font-size:16px\">&nbsp; </span><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;line-height:150%\">刘树根</span><span style=\"font-size:16px\">&nbsp; </span><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;line-height:150%\">刘洪林</span><span style=\"font-size:16px\">&nbsp; </span><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;line-height:150%\">刘可禹</span><span style=\"font-size:16px\">&nbsp; </span><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;line-height:150%\">刘玉章</span><span style=\"font-size:16px\">&nbsp; </span><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;line-height:150%\">卢双舫</span><span style=\"font-size:16px\">&nbsp; </span><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;line-height:150%\">罗晓容</span><span style=\"font-size:16px\">&nbsp; </span><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;line-height:150%\">廖仕孟</span> <span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;line-height:150%\">吕延防</span> &nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;line-height:150%\">解习农</span><span style=\"font-size:16px\">&nbsp; </span><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;line-height:150%\">马新华</span><span style=\"font-size:16px\">&nbsp; </span><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;line-height:150%\">蒙启安</span><span style=\"font-size:16px\">&nbsp; </s